{"tid":730651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"橋本環奈後繼有人？14歲齊藤渚成最新「千年一遇美少女」","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T17:24:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fc28dd17bcb5f4de0bd0d209fc10160260cf58cc","tid":730651,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:34:21.000Z","msg":"日本又出現「千年一遇美少女」了嗎？14歲的日本偶像齊藤渚不但歌聲舞技精湛，亮麗外型更吸引許多粉絲的目光，日前她被粉絲捕捉到一張奇蹟美照，因為裡頭的她真的太可愛無邪，立刻讓她成為網友的討論焦點，甚至還有人點名，她就是女星橋本環奈的接班人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/07/02/1427346-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F1427346-XXL.jpg&h=93bbb0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴著耳機、穿著水手服，會放電的明眸大眼搭配精緻五官，一下就抓住粉絲的目光。<br />\n<br />\n齊藤渚：「來這裡，這裡有位子喔。」<br />\n<br />\n14歲的齊藤渚是日本聲優偶像團體「Equal Love」的團員之一，最近上綜藝節目拍短片，演出扮相太可愛成為日本網友的討論焦點。<br />\n<br />\n齊藤渚：「我是齊藤渚，神奈川縣出生，現在13歲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20161118/s00006/82376ec8d9b08f04ca6de55b7b32f764.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20161118%2Fs00006%2F82376ec8d9b08f04ca6de55b7b32f764.jpg&h=b3ed372a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上她出道以後，亮麗的外型就已經贏得不少粉絲關注，在活動上粉絲捕捉到一張奇蹟美照，她清純可人的面貌更融化粉絲的心，認為她是繼橋本環奈之後，日本演藝圈新一代的「千年一遇」美少女。<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：「小鹿亂撞的心can't see，我是這麼的想你，不要故意使壞好好對著我吧。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管才剛進入演藝圈，齊藤渚已經成功打響名號，這位備受期待的奇蹟美少女，未來會有怎樣的發展也讓粉絲好奇不已。"},{"pid":"673ccae2c560656daa89166a1a4303b8c92850f8","tid":730651,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"屌你放啲乜撚野圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca96aa8f9220e8a127cee6131a7cee9a098f898e","tid":730651,"uid":177089,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/224337_598cfc2848b4b063cace181e976cb207.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F224337_598cfc2848b4b063cace181e976cb207.png&h=0b1eb962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你成隻催狂魔咁"},{"pid":"80b3cfc5d45ccb161c83367c35d5686c95473d88","tid":730651,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"而家d女童顏到小學生咁就比人話靚"},{"pid":"7afd663519133cab31330ed8cbd35e0728eb3c81","tid":730651,"uid":58374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"張圖低質啲喎"},{"pid":"7c7da0f75c5226a9e06832736570c4d68b47c00f","tid":730651,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"同長毛有咩關係先?"},{"pid":"cb2a540f5c1f2aee271549d4eff9da9e99a8caaa","tid":730651,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:46:05.000Z","msg":"唔掂"},{"pid":"9c1f28fa69fe3f54d676ec159817dd0da225f658","tid":730651,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"下"},{"pid":"9c753c75f2ce1e12ba5175b3bee2732e43ccc9fc","tid":730651,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"一線眼"},{"pid":"b3e4c59dc918a3a156428422071ef26c858a8199","tid":730651,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"咁快過左一千年"},{"pid":"27cfc81ac021aa97c37f1bcdbd8ef9b7d7076dcc","tid":730651,"uid":45477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3e4c59dc918a3a156428422071ef26c858a8199","tid":730651,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:04:37.000Z","msg":"咁快過左一千年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img sr